   OLD DOMINION ELECTRIC Cooperative (Glen Allen, Va.) --
John P. Edwards, senior vice president for customer affairs
at Public Service Co. of New Hampshire, was named president
and chief executive officer of this electric cooperative,
effective Aug. 20. He succeeds Guy C. Lewis Jr., who has been
