   Mr. Belford was the subject of a probe by the Federal
Bureau of Investigation. He was accused of using a company
condominium and airplane for personal purposes and of
agreeing to misrepresent the company's financial condition in
annual and quarterly reports.
   The trucking concern is under new management.
